{
    "abstract": "This document specifies a new IPv6 Hop-by-Hop Option that is used to record the Minimum Path MTU (PMTU) along the forward path between a source host to a destination host.  The recorded value can then be communicated back to the source using the return Path MTU field in the Option. ",
